data.description: Welcome home to Mossy Oak - a quaint, small neighborhood with sidewalks, tucked away in a perfect North Augusta location! NO HOA! This lovely home boasts 3,000sqft of living space to include 3 bedrooms, upstairs loft that can be used as a 4th/5th bedroom or office/study, 2.5 bathrooms and a VAST walk-out basement! SOLAR PANELS CONVEY OFFERING TONS OF SAVINGS ON THE POWER BILL! Gorgeous hardwood floors greet you at the entrance and flow throughout the entire main level. Kitchen is well equipped with granite counters, island with seating, pantry and many cabinets! The living room is wide open offering unlimited furniture arrangement. STORAGE ABOUNDS WITH MANY CLOSETS AND FLOORED STORAGE IN THE ATTIC! Upstairs you will find the homes bedrooms and laundry room. The owners suite offers a large room with a cozy tray ceiling and its very own private bathroom featuring a dual sink vanity, shower, separate soaker tub and HUGE walk-in closet. Relax and unwind in the walk-out basement offering low maintenance luxury vinyl floors, tons of space for a game room, man cave, exercise room or even 4th/5th bedroom! Tiered back deck offering unlimited entertaining options overlooking the privacy fenced yard! No neighbors directly behind you. Call today to schedule your private tour!
